| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2741 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f38a05b9-7e19-550c-aa0c-fd8844c5d49d"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
